articles.title: Here’s why analysts soured on Apple this week
articles.description: Apple's manufacturing of iPhones, Macs, and AirPods are being impacted by coronavirus, one analyst said. Meanwhile, Apple TV Plus is having growing pains.

articles.title: Wuhan coronavirus? 2019 nCoV? Naming a new disease
articles.description: In 2015, the World Health Organization issued guidelines discouraging names based on geographic locations, animals, or groups of people.
